Package com.thedemgel.regions.annotations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FeatureCommandArgs  
    FeatureCommandParser
    Used to parse feature commands.
    OnTickParser
    Parser to handle OnTick annotation.
    RegionEventParser  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Intensity
    These are the values for Intensity, an ENUM that is used by the OnTick annotation in Features.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Data
    Annotation to be used to indicate a FIELD that should be saved to the features configuration file.
    EventOrder
    EventOrder annotation tells the EventManager in what order you wish to fire an event.
    FeatureCommand  
    FeatureCommandPermission  
    FeatureName
    Annotation to describe the name of a feature.
    OnTick
    OnTick is a Annotation that needs to be placed on any method in a Feature that needs to fire every tick, multiple methods within a feature can have OnTick placed on them.
    RegionDetector
    Annotation to indicate a Detector class to be executed before the method.
    RegionEvent
    Method Annotation to mark a method to be executed on a given event.
